Sorry.

30:38.855 --> 30:40.100
Parachute...

31:27.611 --> 31:30.019
Firefly from hell!

31:32.199 --> 31:33.741
Big damn bug!

31:46.712 --> 31:48.253
It is you! It is!

31:48.279 --> 31:49.275
A big you!

31:49.465 --> 31:50.766
It's not bad you're big.

31:50.792 --> 31:51.982
You were always big.

31:52.177 --> 31:55.261
Maybe this means you'll be twice as much fun.

31:56.556 --> 31:58.152
What fun we'll have again!

31:58.178 --> 32:00.080
What times!
What great games!

32:03.687 --> 32:05.265
You're a little...

32:07.232 --> 32:08.608
Faerie.

32:13.030 --> 32:13.860
Pixie.

32:14.073 --> 32:16.742
If less is more, there's no end to me, Peter Pan.

32:16.992 --> 32:17.822
- Peter Banning.
- Pan.

32:18.035 --> 32:19.066
- Banning.
- Pan.

32:19.286 --> 32:21.325
Whoever you are, it's still you.

32:21.580 --> 32:24.118
Because only one person has that smell.

32:24.458 --> 32:25.620
Smell?

32:25.834 --> 32:28.241
The smell of someone who's ridden the wind.

32:28.461 --> 32:30.518
The smell of sleeping in trees.

32:30.544 --> 32:33.065
Adventures with Indians and pirates.

32:33.258 --> 32:34.835
Remember?
 The world was ours!

32:34.861 --> 32:36.818
We could do everything or nothing.

32:37.012 --> 32:39.847
I had to be anything because it was always us.

32:43.101 --> 32:45.971
It's happened.
I'm having a nervous breakdown.

32:46.187 --> 32:48.475
Follow me and all will be well.

32:48.689 --> 32:51.082
I'm dying. Heading towards the white light.

32:51.108 --> 32:52.165
I've left my body.

32:52.359 --> 32:53.813
There's my house down there.

32:53.839 --> 32:54.876
There are my feet.

32:55.196 --> 32:56.256
Where are we going?

32:56.282 --> 32:57.842
To save your children!

32:58.116 --> 32:59.409
How do you know about my kids?

32:59.435 --> 33:00.382
Everybody knows!

33:00.576 --> 33:03.861
Hook's got them and you've gotta fight him! Let's fly!

33:10.502 --> 33:11.937
It is true, then.

33:11.963 --> 33:13.481
You did grow up.

33:16.008 --> 33:17.388
I drank poison for you.

33:17.414 --> 33:19.153
You used to call me "Tink."

33:19.344 --> 33:20.896
Have you forgotten everything?

33:20.922 --> 33:22.370
Are you in there, bug?

33:22.639 --> 33:24.928
I'm not a bug. I'm a faerie.

33:29.812 --> 33:31.721
I do not believe in faeries.

33:32.106 --> 33:37.101
Anytime someone says, "I do not believe in faeries," a faerie falls down dead.

33:37.320 --> 33:39.064
I do not believe in faeries!!

33:51.000 --> 33:52.873
My God, I think I killed it.

33:54.294 --> 33:56.964
Are you alive, little bug?
Look out!

33:57.548 --> 34:00.335
Clap your hands, Peter.

34:00.551 --> 34:02.045
It's the only way to save me.

34:02.553 --> 34:03.928
Clap...

34:05.347 --> 34:06.627
Louder.

34:07.724 --> 34:09.135
Louder, Peter!

34:12.228 --> 34:13.722
I'm clapping!

34:14.647 --> 34:16.306
Oh, God, you're alive!

34:16.734 --> 34:18.809
All right.
Now, who am I?

34:26.743 --> 34:30.112
You're a Freudian hallucination of my mother.

34:30.329 --> 34:33.579
I don't know why you have wings, but you have lovely legs.

34:33.791 --> 34:35.618
What am I saying?
I'm an orphan.

34:35.876 --> 34:38.344
I've never taken drugs. I missed the '60s.

34:38.370 --> 34:39.601
I was an accountant.

34:40.215 --> 34:41.080
Guess again!

34:43.801 --> 34:45.460
Look, stars!

34:45.678 --> 34:46.958
That's right, Peter.

34:47.179 --> 34:50.215
Second star to the right and straight on till morning.

34:51.350 --> 34:52.927
Never Land!

35:54.411 --> 35:56.534
What a nightmare!

36:13.513 --> 36:16.182
Roll out! Roll out!

36:27.568 --> 36:30.984
Lovely fish! Fresh fish!

36:31.197 --> 36:35.111
We keep the eyes in so they'll see you through the week!

36:39.871 --> 36:42.825
Excuse me.
Is there a pay phone around here?

36:43.416 --> 36:44.331
That is so real.

36:44.543 --> 36:45.622
Peter, get back here!

36:45.836 --> 36:47.295
Get down!
Get low!

36:47.629 --> 36:48.661
Hide!

36:51.883 --> 36:53.792
If it ain't the Mother Inferior.

36:54.010 --> 36:55.802
Gentlemen, I'm looking for someone.

36:56.179 --> 36:59.299
I fancy them shiny shoes for my booties.

36:59.515 --> 37:01.591
I think you can get them at Armani.

37:02.727 --> 37:05.349
Tink! Tink! Help!

37:08.358 --> 37:10.066
Don't get no blood on them boots!

37:10.401 --> 37:11.860
They's mine!

37:12.070 --> 37:13.729
Help me! Tinkerbell!

37:15.198 --> 37:16.395
You pixie devil!

37:20.452 --> 37:22.860
Please don't! I have a bad back!

37:24.790 --> 37:26.830
You pixie devil!

37:34.716 --> 37:36.259
Are you related to Mighty Mouse?

37:41.723 --> 37:44.178
If you insist on seeing Hook...

37:44.392 --> 37:45.767
...do exactly what I say.

37:45.977 --> 37:49.228
Your left arm is dead and hangs lifeless at your side.

37:49.815 --> 37:52.899
Lean on the crutch! Left foot turned in.

37:53.151 --> 37:56.021
Tilt your head and glare with your good eye!

37:56.321 --> 37:59.772
Now crack your mouth and drool. Now growl!

38:00.032 --> 38:00.862
Growl!

38:01.075 --> 38:01.701
How are you?

38:01.727 --> 38:02.927
Not bad, and you?

38:03.160 --> 38:04.571
Not bad!

38:25.432 --> 38:27.487
Put your faces on, girls.

38:27.513 --> 38:28.992
Here comes Smee!

38:33.190 --> 38:34.649
Follow that Hook!

38:34.983 --> 38:37.308
Make way for the Hook!

38:39.070 --> 38:41.359
Me mother loves that Hook!

38:49.831 --> 38:51.491
Give us the Hook!

38:53.793 --> 38:55.252
Give us the Hook!

39:24.322 --> 39:27.406
Good morning, Never Land!

39:27.617 --> 39:30.701
Good morning, Mr. Smee!

39:31.204 --> 39:33.826
Tie down the main mast, mateys.

39:34.499 --> 39:36.788
Because here he is! The cunning kingfish!

39:37.460 --> 39:38.705
The brave barracuda!

39:39.921 --> 39:43.621
A man so deep, he's almost unfathomable.

39:45.384 --> 39:50.295
A man so quick, he's even fast asleep!

39:50.764 --> 39:51.796
Thank you!

39:52.016 --> 39:53.890
Let's give him a very big hand...

39:54.102 --> 39:56.343
...because he's only got one.

39:58.064 --> 40:01.598
I give you the steel-handed stingray...

40:01.817 --> 40:04.652
...Captain James Hook!

40:04.903 --> 40:06.777
Hook! Hook! Hook! Hook!

40:15.956 --> 40:17.865
See how greatly the men favor you, sir?

40:18.083 --> 40:19.791
The pealing spawn.

40:19.817 --> 40:21.808
How I despise them!

40:22.003 --> 40:23.877
Go get 'em, captain!

40:27.800 --> 40:29.081
Thank you!

40:31.179 --> 40:36.304
Well, my stupid, sorry, parasitic sacks of entrails...

40:39.062 --> 40:40.889
Revenge is mine.

40:42.607 --> 40:44.017
Long live the Hook!

40:44.233 --> 40:47.269
I baited that Hook and now I'm proud to announce...

40:47.486 --> 40:49.360
...we have his children.

40:49.905 --> 40:53.025
My God! Jack and Maggie.

40:55.118 --> 40:57.491
Finally I'm going to kill Peter Pan...

40:57.705 --> 41:02.248
...that cocky boy who cut off my hand and fed it to the crocodile!

41:02.835 --> 41:06.453
And who killed that cunning crocodile? Who stuffed him?

41:06.672 --> 41:08.331
Who made him into a quiet clock?

41:08.548 --> 41:11.584
Who went to the other world and stole Pan's children?

41:12.260 --> 41:14.549
And who didn't believe I could do it?

41:15.263 --> 41:16.841
Who doubted me?

41:17.933 --> 41:20.175
Who amongst us does not belong?

41:20.894 --> 41:22.721
Someone here does not belong.

41:22.938 --> 41:25.607
Stranger amongst the loyal, I'll weed you out.

41:28.818 --> 41:29.933
You!

41:34.156 --> 41:35.615
You!

41:39.829 --> 41:41.620
Where's the carpet, Smee?

41:41.831 --> 41:43.325
Sorry, sir.

41:46.085 --> 41:47.283
You!

41:47.753 --> 41:49.461
You! That's right, you!

41:49.672 --> 41:51.960
No, not you! Not you.

41:53.091 --> 41:54.372
You.

41:55.260 --> 41:56.256
You!

41:59.181 --> 42:02.716
You bet against me bringing Pan back here, didn't you?

42:04.895 --> 42:07.101
Tell your captain the truth.

42:11.151 --> 42:13.108
Say it. Say it.

42:14.070 --> 42:15.232
I did.

42:15.488 --> 42:17.445
- You made a boo-boo.
- I did.

42:18.574 --> 42:19.751
The Boo Box.

42:19.777 --> 42:21.933
Not the Boo Box!

42:39.303 --> 42:40.466
Boo!

42:44.809 --> 42:46.137
Put me down!

42:46.352 --> 42:48.294
I want my mommy!

42:48.320 --> 42:50.504
I want my daddy!

42:50.981 --> 42:52.808
Hello, children.

42:53.024 --> 42:55.432
Comfy? Cozy?

42:55.694 --> 42:58.363
Those are my kids!

42:58.571 --> 43:00.480
Those are my kids!

43:04.369 --> 43:06.942
Everything's gonna be all right.

43:08.540 --> 43:09.338
It's all right.

43:09.364 --> 43:10.107
Daddy's here.

43:10.583 --> 43:14.581
I want those kids out of that net or you better get an attorney.

43:14.796 --> 43:15.875
Who are you?

43:16.088 --> 43:17.183
I'm Peter Banning.

43:17.209 --> 43:18.485
I want my children.

43:18.674 --> 43:19.872
Those are your?

43:20.134 --> 43:21.592
These are your children?

43:21.927 --> 43:22.959
And you're?

43:23.179 --> 43:24.093
You're Peter?

43:24.305 --> 43:26.345
You're Peter?
 No!

43:27.100 --> 43:27.883
You're Peter?

43:27.909 --> 43:30.078
Is there an echo in here?
 Yes!

43:30.269 --> 43:32.807
My great and worthy opponent?

43:34.982 --> 43:36.180
Who is this impostor?

43:36.400 --> 43:39.187
Peter flogging flying Pan!

43:40.570 --> 43:41.832
I'm not Peter Pan.

43:41.858 --> 43:43.680
I am just an ordinary...

43:43.908 --> 43:46.114
I've got a sworn affidavit by a T. Bell.

43:46.410 --> 43:48.073
I've got his medical history.

43:48.099 --> 43:49.934
I even got his dental records.

43:50.831 --> 43:53.286
Are you trying to do me out of my job?

43:53.500 --> 43:54.830
May I show you something?

43:54.856 --> 43:55.813
Will you let go?

43:56.002 --> 43:57.165
Release him.

43:57.378 --> 43:58.458
May I show you this?

43:58.484 --> 43:59.941
Will you shut him up.

44:03.843 --> 44:05.226
Captain, put these on.

44:05.252 --> 44:07.072
I want to see the scar.

44:07.263 --> 44:08.592
The hypertrophy.

44:09.390 --> 44:12.806
Here's where you sliced him during the Tiger Lily incident.

44:13.019 --> 44:14.133
That's my appendix!

44:14.353 --> 44:15.385
What's this?

44:15.605 --> 44:17.002
Faerie footprints.

44:17.028 --> 44:20.754
He's Peter Pan or I've got a dead man's dinghy.

44:23.946 --> 44:25.773
Is it you?

44:26.365 --> 44:29.532
My great and worthy opponent?

44:30.327 --> 44:32.450
But it can't be.

44:33.330 --> 44:36.035
Not this pitiful, spineless, pasty, bloated...

44:36.291 --> 44:39.327
...codfish I see before me.

44:39.836 --> 44:42.872
You're not even a shadow of Peter Pan.

44:46.218 --> 44:49.384
You have an obligation to clarify this Pan problem.

44:49.596 --> 44:50.426
This disaster.

44:50.639 --> 44:52.512
- Which must be remedied.
- Expediently.

44:52.724 --> 44:53.612
I want my children.

44:53.638 --> 44:55.038
The stakes can be no higher.

44:55.226 --> 44:58.181
For me, sir, they could have sunk no lower.

44:58.207 --> 44:59.580
And I want my war!

44:59.772 --> 45:01.432
Blow him out of the water!

45:01.941 --> 45:04.064
Daddy's handling this. It's okay.

45:05.569 --> 45:06.851
Pick up your weapon.

45:11.909 --> 45:13.238
How much?

45:22.252 --> 45:24.577
Hoist and raise the kiddies!

45:32.179 --> 45:34.694
I'll make you a deal, Mr. Chairman.

45:34.720 --> 45:35.869
Fly up there...

45:36.058 --> 45:40.102
...and touch the fingers of your children, and I'll set them free.

45:40.437 --> 45:41.516
I can't fly.

45:41.729 --> 45:42.954
Explode out of there!

45:42.980 --> 45:44.062
Stop this charade!

45:44.088 --> 45:45.254
Free your children!

45:49.654 --> 45:51.279
I beg your pardon?

45:53.450 --> 45:54.825
You must be joking.

45:56.619 --> 46:00.451
Peter Pan has a real problem with heights.

46:01.165 --> 46:03.371
I'm not Peter Pan.

46:03.709 --> 46:05.504
It's okay. Hang on, son.

46:05.530 --> 46:07.399
I'm coming, sweetheart.

46:07.588 --> 46:09.233
Somebody give me a hand.

46:09.259 --> 46:10.698
I already have.

46:20.434 --> 46:21.809
Save us, Daddy!

46:22.019 --> 46:24.426
"Save me, Daddy!"

46:25.480 --> 46:26.831
We know who you are!

46:26.857 --> 46:29.289
What new game is this, Peter? Fly!

46:29.484 --> 46:31.477
Stop pretending!

46:34.614 --> 46:36.524
Fly! I know it's you!

46:42.163 --> 46:45.080
Be the Pan you are. Fly!

46:45.374 --> 46:47.201
Fly! Think a happy thought.

46:47.668 --> 46:51.582
Just touch our fingers and we'll be able to go home.

46:52.048 --> 46:55.748
Touch them, Peter, and it's all been just a bad dream!

46:55.968 --> 46:58.424
Just reach out and touch them!

47:01.015 --> 47:03.054
Flap your arm and fly!

47:05.602 --> 47:07.013
Reach!

47:07.271 --> 47:08.231
Come on, Daddy.

47:08.257 --> 47:09.537
Mommy could do it.

47:14.445 --> 47:15.579
I don't understand.

47:15.605 --> 47:16.772
Why doesn't he fly?

47:16.798 --> 47:18.170
He's a fop Peter Pan!

47:18.365 --> 47:21.117
He's Peter Pan, all right, captain.

47:21.326 --> 47:25.703
He's been away from Never Land so long, his mind's been gentrified.

47:25.914 --> 47:27.990
He's forgotten everything.

47:33.839 --> 47:36.164
Please don't give up.

47:49.144 --> 47:50.769
I want to go home.

47:54.399 --> 47:58.896
Gentlemen, I'm afraid I have decided to cancel the war.

48:00.030 --> 48:03.067
He can't fly, but he can swim!

48:03.575 --> 48:04.951
Kill them.

48:05.661 --> 48:06.823
Kill them all.

48:08.246 --> 48:09.740
Bring on the plank!

48:12.959 --> 48:17.040
And I never want to hear the name Peter Pan again!

48:19.508 --> 48:20.847
What about the name Hook?

48:20.873 --> 48:23.067
Do you want to be remembered as a bully?

48:23.261 --> 48:26.096
Or as the great warrior who defeated a heroic Pan?

48:28.307 --> 48:32.969
One week and I'll get him in shape, and you can have your dirty old war.

48:33.771 --> 48:35.219
It's a trick, captain!

48:35.245 --> 48:38.340
Let me blast that buzzing vixen to pixie hell!

48:41.737 --> 48:43.979
You promised people the war of the century.

48:44.198 --> 48:47.733
Your whole life has been building to this. Mortal combat, glory!

48:47.993 --> 48:49.191
Hook versus Pan!

48:49.411 --> 48:51.867
That is not Pan.

49:05.594 --> 49:06.543
Two days.

49:07.095 --> 49:09.551
Four. Bare minimum for a decent Pan.

49:10.306 --> 49:11.421
Three. Final offer.

49:12.600 --> 49:13.763
Done.

49:15.394 --> 49:17.351
And you'd better deliver, Miss Bell...

49:17.563 --> 49:22.226
...or no amount of clapping will bring you back from where I will send you.

49:24.654 --> 49:25.603
Hear me, men.

49:25.822 --> 49:28.776
I've decided that the so-called Pan...

49:29.033 --> 49:32.484
...will return in three days to commence the arbitrament of the sword.

49:32.703 --> 49:33.818
Smee, translate.

49:34.038 --> 49:35.911
In three days we'll have a war.

49:36.123 --> 49:39.408
A battle between good and evil, to the death.

49:46.050 --> 49:47.758
Help me!

51:30.317 --> 51:31.515
Snow!

51:35.489 --> 51:36.734
What?

51:37.616 --> 51:38.861
What?

51:51.546 --> 51:52.791
Help!

51:58.011 --> 51:59.042
Get me down!

52:03.849 --> 52:05.427
Oh, you're alive!

52:05.893 --> 52:07.174
Oh, get me down!

52:07.520 --> 52:08.551
I believe!

52:08.771 --> 52:09.491
Lost Boys!

52:09.517 --> 52:10.955
Lost Boys!
Wake up!

52:18.197 --> 52:19.442
Pan's back!

52:19.698 --> 52:22.154
Lost Boys! Lost Boys! Wake up!

52:23.410 --> 52:25.283
That was my pillow!

52:26.579 --> 52:28.075
I'm up.

52:30.376 --> 52:32.582
Wake up, you sleepyheads!

52:33.086 --> 52:36.289
Pan's back!
Pan's back! Pan!

52:46.224 --> 52:47.468
Pan!

52:52.480 --> 52:54.888
Who's the shrub?

52:56.526 --> 52:57.771
Bangerang!

53:06.452 --> 53:08.076
That ain't Peter Pan.

53:08.328 --> 53:09.194
He's old.

53:09.455 --> 53:10.534
He's fat!

53:10.790 --> 53:12.498
Not so fat to me.

53:13.042 --> 53:15.959
He's an old, fat grandpa man.

53:21.675 --> 53:22.873
Rufio!

53:31.393 --> 53:33.267
That is so dangerous.

53:37.524 --> 53:39.931
That's enough!

53:40.944 --> 53:42.319
Okay, mister. All right.

53:42.528 --> 53:43.577
The show's over.

53:43.603 --> 53:45.044
Put that thing away!

53:45.239 --> 53:47.777
Put it down before you poke somebody's eye out.

53:47.992 --> 53:49.549
You're not old enough to shave.

53:49.575 --> 53:51.433
What are you doing with that sword?

53:51.621 --> 53:54.146
This is an insurance nightmare!
What's this?

53:54.172 --> 53:55.893
<i>Lord of the Flies</i> preschool?

53:56.501 --> 53:58.244
Where are your parents?

53:58.461 --> 54:00.287
Who's in charge here?

54:03.132 --> 54:07.081
No, Mr. Skunkhead-with-too-much-mousse, you're just a punk kid.

54:07.344 --> 54:09.383
I want to speak to a grownup!

54:09.638 --> 54:11.511
All grownups are pirates!

54:11.723 --> 54:12.554
Excuse me?

54:13.184 --> 54:14.975
We kill pirates.

54:16.270 --> 54:17.894
I'm not a pirate.

54:18.272 --> 54:20.845
It so happens I am a lawyer.

54:21.900 --> 54:23.939
Kill the lawyer!

54:24.861 --> 54:26.853
I'm not that kind of lawyer.

54:50.010 --> 54:51.884
I've been shot!

54:56.475 --> 54:57.507
Help!

54:57.727 --> 54:59.802
Help me, somebody!

55:04.816 --> 55:07.272
Boys, listen!
He married Wendy's granddaughter!

55:07.486 --> 55:08.695
Hook's kidnapped his kids.

55:08.721 --> 55:09.883
He's just out of shape.

55:10.113 --> 55:12.438
We have to make him bangerang!

55:12.991 --> 55:14.983
No, no! Please stop!

55:16.370 --> 55:17.912
Why are you doing this to me?

55:18.372 --> 55:20.554
Rufio, you're the best with a sword.

55:20.580 --> 55:21.730
Please teach him.

55:21.917 --> 55:24.205
We gotta make him remember.

55:37.515 --> 55:38.345
Excuse me.

55:52.779 --> 55:54.060
Help me!

55:54.322 --> 55:56.114
Not you!

56:21.725 --> 56:23.053
Oh, my! A wall.

56:34.570 --> 56:36.858
Lost Boys, stop! Stop it!

56:43.829 --> 56:44.659
Play!

56:46.457 --> 56:47.571
Play.

57:11.564 --> 57:14.731
You're dead, jolly man.

57:15.359 --> 57:16.948
He can't do those things.

57:16.974 --> 57:19.133
He can't even play simple games.

57:19.363 --> 57:22.234
Hook has got his kids, and I've got three days...

57:22.450 --> 57:24.088
...to get him ready to fight.

57:24.114 --> 57:25.808
And I need everybody's help.

57:26.037 --> 57:29.370
Peter Pan's got kids?

57:36.922 --> 57:41.050
He can't fly, fight or crow.

57:43.053 --> 57:47.051
If any of you says this here scug ain't Peter Pan...

57:47.266 --> 57:48.511
...cross the line.

57:55.899 --> 57:58.187
What? I'll be right back.

57:59.444 --> 58:00.642
What?

58:00.862 --> 58:03.104
You are embarrassing me!

59:16.810 --> 59:19.266
Oh, there you are, Peter!

