01:06:23.932 --> 01:06:27.017
<i>Ain't no time to celebrate</i>

01:06:27.269 --> 01:06:30.305
<i>You are old and overweight</i>

01:06:30.606 --> 01:06:33.642
<i>Gotta lose a million pounds</i>

01:06:33.859 --> 01:06:36.046
<i>Get your fat butt off the ground</i>

01:06:36.072 --> 01:06:38.462
<i>Reach on down and touch your toes</i>

01:06:38.697 --> 01:06:42.030
<i>How long since you looked at those?</i>

01:06:42.283 --> 01:06:43.564
<i>Shape up</i>

01:06:43.785 --> 01:06:45.279
<i>Lose weight</i>

01:06:45.494 --> 01:06:46.823
<i>Get thin</i>

01:06:47.038 --> 01:06:47.868
