02:03:08.687 --> 02:03:11.605
I never want to see your face in Never Land again.

02:03:19.197 --> 02:03:20.160
Peter, look out!

02:03:20.186 --> 02:03:22.472
Fools, James Hook is Never Land!

02:03:24.285 --> 02:03:27.121
Whenever children read, it will say:

