Hook's gone.

02:04:34.687 --> 02:04:37.392
Hook's gone! Hook's gone!

02:04:40.693 --> 02:04:42.769
Bangerang!

02:04:46.156 --> 02:04:46.986
No more Hook!

02:04:47.241 --> 02:04:50.444
No more Hook! No more Hook!

02:04:53.914 --> 02:04:56.156
Hurray for Pan the Man!

02:05:03.882 --> 02:05:05.958
What's wrong, Peter?

02:05:06.342 --> 02:05:07.341
I can't stay.

02:05:07.367 --> 02:05:11.363
I've done what I came to do, and now I have to go back.

02:05:15.143 --> 02:05:18.263
Tink, make my kids glow.

02:05:27.446 --> 02:05:32.156
Jack, Maggie, all you have to do is think one happy thought...

02:05:32.410 --> 02:05:34.118
...and you'll fly like me.

02:05:38.249 --> 02:05:39.447
Mommy!

02:05:40.793 --> 02:05:42.251
My dad...

02:05:43.379 --> 02:05:44.956
...Peter Pan.

02:05:49.134 --> 02:05:51.210
Tink, you know the way.

02:05:51.512 --> 02:05:53.303
I'll be just behind you.

02:06:15.493 --> 02:06:19.158
Don't leave us, Peter, and don't say goodbye.

02:06:19.455 --> 02:06:20.866
What's "goodbye"?

02:06:21.124 --> 02:06:22.322
It's going away.

02:06:22.348 --> 02:06:23.770
That's what it is.

02:06:24.001 --> 02:06:25.910
Forgetting about us all over again.

02:06:26.128 --> 02:06:27.546
You're all my Lost Boys.

02:06:27.572 --> 02:06:28.988
I'll never forget you.

02:06:29.673 --> 02:06:30.918
Never.

02:06:34.262 --> 02:06:36.254
So who do I leave in charge?

02:07:12.214 --> 02:07:15.666
I want you to take care of everyone who's smaller than you.

02:07:16.803 --> 02:07:18.961
Then who do I look after?

02:07:19.931 --> 02:07:21.508
Never Bugs.

02:07:22.808 --> 02:07:24.433
Little ones.

02:07:46.832 --> 02:07:50.117
That was a great game.

02:07:50.794 --> 02:07:52.786
<i>Thank you for believing.</i>

02:08:28.413 --> 02:08:29.872
I know her.

02:08:30.916 --> 02:08:33.537
She looks like an angel.

02:08:33.752 --> 02:08:36.159
Let's not wake her yet.

02:09:24.802 --> 02:09:28.502
My dear child, have you been up all night?

02:09:29.640 --> 02:09:33.091
I see them in their beds so often in my dreams.

02:09:33.685 --> 02:09:35.891
When I wake up, they're still there.

02:10:19.062 --> 02:10:20.077
Tink?

02:10:20.103 --> 02:10:22.538
Tink? Tink?

02:10:31.741 --> 02:10:32.571
Hello.

02:10:35.745 --> 02:10:37.498
Having trouble with the misses?

02:10:37.524 --> 02:10:39.898
You will have, by the time you get home.

02:10:46.172 --> 02:10:47.002
Tink!

02:10:49.008 --> 02:10:50.464
Say it, Peter.

02:10:50.490 --> 02:10:52.568
Say it and mean it.

02:10:54.096 --> 02:10:55.887
I believe in faeries.

02:10:56.390 --> 02:10:59.225
Do you know that place between sleep and awake...

02:10:59.726 --> 02:11:01.683
...where you still remember dreaming?

02:11:04.105 --> 02:11:06.313
That's where I'll always love you...

02:11:07.318 --> 02:11:08.978
...Peter Pan.

02:11:11.822 --> 02:11:13.613
That's where I'll be waiting.

02:11:33.676 --> 02:11:35.170
Nana!

02:11:35.386 --> 02:11:36.621
Oh, give us a kiss!

02:11:36.647 --> 02:11:38.661
Come here, you drool machine!

02:11:46.396 --> 02:11:47.807
Tink?

02:12:05.623 --> 02:12:08.993
Brad! Hi! Have you been holding this long?

02:12:10.003 --> 02:12:12.094
I'm incredible! Yeah.

02:12:12.120 --> 02:12:13.314
Never Land!

02:12:14.591 --> 02:12:15.970
Lost Boys.
Jim Hook.

02:12:15.996 --> 02:12:17.295
Duel to the death.

02:12:17.321 --> 02:12:19.053
I'll fill you in later.

02:12:19.262 --> 02:12:21.005
Listen, I'd love to chat...

02:12:21.264 --> 02:12:23.470
...but I gotta climb a drainpipe now.

02:12:24.100 --> 02:12:26.664
Why? Because I ran out of faerie dust.

02:12:26.690 --> 02:12:29.119
If not, I would've flown up. Why!!

02:12:35.445 --> 02:12:36.853
There were pirates..!

02:12:36.879 --> 02:12:38.554
And monsters there!

02:12:39.281 --> 02:12:40.657
Just like you said!

02:12:40.866 --> 02:12:42.241
Granny Wendy!

02:12:43.369 --> 02:12:44.317
Let me in!

02:12:45.037 --> 02:12:46.412
Please.

02:12:48.999 --> 02:12:51.372
Excuse me, do you have an appointment?

02:12:54.004 --> 02:12:57.040
What did I tell you about this window?

02:12:57.341 --> 02:12:58.716
Always keep it open!

02:13:00.552 --> 02:13:03.506
Never, ever, ever close...

02:13:23.074 --> 02:13:24.568
I have to take this.

02:13:24.784 --> 02:13:29.077
Have you ever known what it's like to feel the exhilaration of really flying?

02:13:29.329 --> 02:13:31.037
Feel this.

02:13:32.040 --> 02:13:33.535
Where have you been?

02:13:33.751 --> 02:13:34.996
Fly me, Daddy, fly me!

02:13:35.211 --> 02:13:36.468
Anytime, Maggie.

02:13:36.494 --> 02:13:38.770
To infinity and back again.

02:13:39.340 --> 02:13:41.048
Hello, Peter.

02:13:41.717 --> 02:13:45.002
I missed the adventure again, didn't I?

02:13:46.680 --> 02:13:48.756
I think these belong to you.

